message:
Hello everyone! 
Community Team is hosting a tailgate this weekend before the 11AM Gopher game. I'll be posting a link to the official event within the next few days. However, this post is to ask if anyone is willing and able to help with tasks such as:
-setting up
-making pancakes
-pouring drinks
-transporting food to the designated location (possibly need a car)
-cleaning up
If you are interested please message me. Thank you and I hope you are all having a great week! :)
